tableInfo.sql: select T_CK_FYFS.mc as YSMC,V_DW.JM as FFMC,T_QX_DW.mc as JSDWMC, T_CK_CRKQD.Bh,T_CK_CRKQD.Cxsgin,T_CK_CRKQD.Fjh,T_CK_CRKQD.Jh,t_Ck_Crkqd.Xh,t_Ck_Crkqd.Jwh, T_CK_CRKQD.Dj,T_CK_CRKQD.Zj,T_CK_CRKQD.Hl,T_CK_CRKQD.Tzs,T_CK_CRKQD.Sl,T_CK_CRKQD.Jjs,T_CK_CRKQD.Ckdm,T_CK_CRKQD.Jxqn,T_CK_CRKQD.Jxqxs, T_CK_CRKQD.Ccrq,T_CK_CRKQD.Ysrq,T_CK_CRKQD.Smzt,T_CK_CRKQD.Zsmn,T_CK_CRKQD.Zsmxs,T_CK_CRKQD.Zsmxh,T_CK_CRKQD.Zsmql,T_CK_CRKQD.Yfrq,T_CK_CRKQD.Yfqx, T_CK_CRKQD.Fxrq,T_CK_CRKQD.Fxsmn,T_CK_CRKQD.Fxsmxs,T_CK_CRKQD.Fxcs,T_CK_CRKQD.Sbqxn,T_CK_CRKQD.Sbqxxs,T_CK_CRKQD.Bz, T_CK_CRKQD.Zfxxs,T_CK_CRKQD.Bczfxxs,T_CK_CRKQD.Bcfxxs,T_CK_CRKQD.Zxhcs,T_CK_CRKQD.Bczxhcs,T_CK_CRKQD.Bcxhcs,T_CK_CRKQD.Zqlcs,T_CK_CRKQD.Bczqlcs, T_CK_CRKQD.Bcqlcs,T_CK_CRKQD.Yfcs,T_CK_CRKQD.Zyfcs ,T_JH_JX.mc as JXMC,T_JH.mc as JHMC, T_CK_CRK.WH,T_CK_CRK.YJ,T_XT_JLDW.MC JLDW,T_JH_ZL.MC as ZLMC,T_XT_BZLB.HL NEWHL,T_XT_BZLB.MC BZMC ,T_XT_ZD.MC ZDMC,SRR,PZR,BGY,GZ,T_JH_ZYLX.MC ZYLX,T_CK_CRKQD.Rkrq,T_CK_CRKQD.jx from T_CK_CRKQD left join T_CK_CRK on T_CK_CRK.BH=T_CK_CRKQD.BH left join T_JH_JX on T_JH_JX.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.Jx left join T_JH on T_JH.id=T_CK_CRKQD.jh AND T_JH.JX=T_CK_CRKQD.JX LEFT JOIN T_JH_ZYLX ON T_JH_ZYLX.ID=T_JH.ZYLX left join T_CK_FYFS on T_CK_FYFS.id=T_CK_CRK.Ysfs left join V_DW on V_DW.ID=T_CK_CRK.FFDW left join T_QX_DW on T_QX_DW.id=T_CK_CRK.jsdw LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW ON T_XT_JLDW.ID=T_JH.DW left join T_JH_ZL on T_JH_Zl.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.ZL LEFT JOIN T_XT_BZLB ON T_XT_BZLB.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.BBZ LEFT JOIN T_XT_ZD ON T_XT_ZD.ZDID=T_CK_CRKQD.ZDDM and T_XT_ZD.DWID=T_CK_CRKQD.Dwid where 1=1 AND CXSGIN=0 and T_CK_CRKQD.lb like '2001%' ORDER BY T_CK_CRKQD.BH DESC
